    "Among the fully-unlabeled clients, (13) min L() = sup (x k e, y e) + unsup (x k r) (14) min L() = A ∑ a=1 a L a ( a) + B ∑ b=1 b L b ( b),L b can be a mean-teacher or contrastive loss.",
